                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-145-off819 t18320216-145-crimeloc822"></join>. On the 21st of January these shoes hung on my door-post - the prisoner came and asked the price of them; I said if he wanted a pair he had better come in - he then took them, and ran away: I pursued, and came up to him - he put them down, and struck me several times - these are the shoes.</p>
